author: Deepika Jayaram
title: Manju in high voltage cop look in Vettah
text:
Since Manju Warrier made her second innings in the Malayalam film industry, the characters she has enacted on screen stood out for the substantial woman centric roles they were.
The first look of Manju's next Vettah is out and the actor is clothed in high attitude and character, with an all new cop avatar.
Seen in high pony and tucked in shirts, Manju is seen carrying the cop's look with flair.
